{
  "texts": [
    "However, there are studies in relevant fields.",
    "Therefore, to acknowledge the existing relevant work, we explored and reviewed the literature in the following topics: scientific thinking and reasoning, medical reasoning, literature-based discovery, and field study on scientific thinking and discovery.",
    "Under each topic, we introduce a literature review of the topic and what we can learn from these studies.",
    "A comprehensive summary of the four topics concludes the literature review section.",
    "We then introduce our study objectives before summarizing the methods and results of our study."
  ]
}